74–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Thomas  Robert Mirfield ,Esq, was born about 1247, in Halifax, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"about 1247–":"umbes 1247–Surnud","1267–Female":"1267–Surnud","1247–Male":"1247–Surnud","1247":"1247","1267":"1267","about 1247":"umbes 1247","Mirfield, Halifax, Yorkshire, England":"Halifax, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1247–":"noin 1247–Kuollut","1267–Female":"1267–Kuollut","1247–Male":"1247–Kuollut","1247":"1247","1267":"1267","about 1247":"noin 1247","Mirfield, Halifax, Yorkshire, England":"Halifax, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1247–":"environ 1247–Décédé","1267–Female":"1267–Décédée","1247–Male":"1247–Décédé","1247":"1247","1267":"1267","about 1247":"environ 1247","Mirfield, Halifax, Yorkshire, England":"Halifax, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Thomas  Robert Mirfield ,Esq, est né environ 1247, à Halifax, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"about 1247–":"um 1247–Verstorben","1267–Female":"1267–Verstorben","1247–Male":"1247–Verstorben","1247":"1247","1267":"1267","about 1247":"um 1247","Mirfield, Halifax, Yorkshire, England":"Halifax, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Thomas  Robert Mirfield ,Esq, wurde um 1247 in Halifax, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"about 1247–":"about 1247–Desede","1267–Female":"1267–Desede","1247–Male":"1247–Desede","1247":"1247","1267":"1267","about 1247":"about 1247","Mirfield, Halifax, Yorkshire, England":"Halifax, Yorkshire, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"about 1247–":"1247 körül–elhunyt","1267–Female":"1267–elhunyt","1247–Male":"1247–elhunyt","1247":"1247","1267":"1